{"tid":2488894,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"連coinbase利好消息都出哂, 今次bitcoin應該見頂了","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:19:33.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b78f21d8772ef0a186aea6a0793b3eddbce64e2","tid":2488894,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔準備幫人接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6萬蚊BTC<br />\n2千蚊ETH<br />\n600蚊BNB<br />\n<br />\n全部都係騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69ab477445604802caf8b8c7e4ed3b8d2704d4d","tid":2488894,"uid":393710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"Bin C準備<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4845c2d6f296824c2cc84b182cff7b76e34a6fb7","tid":2488894,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"BTC 125% short<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e417ca54a3a8435e6fc31b233b49326a784bd","tid":2488894,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"絕對係 有貨好走 一個月後btc1000蚊都冇 2021年仲有人信加密貨幣"},{"pid":"c531d8202f5d8a903d80795db837052a3ee426a9","tid":2488894,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"btc唔清楚<br />\n但coinbase 係睇淡<br />\n<br />\n班大戶上市前<br />\n半年炒高左幾多倍&nbsp;差不多20倍&nbsp;&nbsp;如果真係600蚊開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】準備在納斯達克交易所直接上市的Coinbase，上市前估值急升。根據該公司向美國證交會（SEC）提交的申報文件顯示，在截至3月15日的第一季，Coinbase的股票在私募市場的加權平均交易價格為343.58美元，意味該公司的估值達到680億美元（5304億港元）。<br />\n最新估值5304億 超紐交所母公司<br />\n<br />\n相比去年第三季，該公司在私募市場的加權平均交易價格為每股28.83美元，當時公司估值僅53億美元。最新估值，較半年前增長12倍，超越紐交所母公司洲際交易所集團（ICE）、納斯達克交易所和倫交所（LSE）的市值，較芝加哥商品交易所集團（CME Group）僅少40億美元，突顯其估值隨比特幣價格飛漲。比特幣價格昨在5.8萬美元水平徘徊。"}]}